metadata.name: revivescere no. 1
metadata.description:
The first piece in my debut collection, “revivescere”, in my new ongoing series, I’m The Artist, Too, is a demand for copyright reform. Subjects of artistic works deserve rights to anything created using their likeness. We deserve a say.

Read more about the project at https://www.imtheartisttoo.com/

Visit https://opensea.io/collection/revivescere to see more pieces from this collection

In collaboration with Soulcraft  https://linktr.ee/_soulcraft_
